headline: Erie Indemnity (NASDAQ:ERIE) Reports Sales Below Analyst Estimates In Q2 Earnings
summary: Insurance management company Erie Indemnity (NASDAQ:ERIE) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, but sales rose 7% year on year to $1.06 billion. Its GAAP profit of $3.34 per share was 5.9% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
